Description:
    - This 00README file describes how the "models_arch-rasp_thrs-opt-{---}" case was designed.

Procedure (followed for each output):
    - Architecture Rasp et al. (2018)

    - Threshold (optimized threshold for each output). Method:
        Analysis folder: "notebooks_SHERPA_thrs_optimization_per_output"
        Scripts: 
            - "Create_optimized_threshold_dict_mse.ipynb"
            - "Create_optimized_threshold_dict_r2.ipynb"
        Config:
            SHE_alg    = 'GridSearch'
            method     = 'sig' # 'sig'; 'aic'
            sig        = 2
            pdf        = True # Quantile-based threshold
            
            ## Explore optimal quantile-thrs per output
            SHE_path   = f'./hyperparameter_tuning_{SHE_alg}_threshold_SHERPA/'
            SHE_date   = '2022041[6,7]_*'
